channel.title: Items disappeared
channel.description: Was at my house in world 2 and typed /spawn so that I could go back to world 1. It told me "You do not have permission to go here" I was like.."Did I type it wrong" So I typed it again and it told me I couldn't use it for another 23 hours 59 minutes. Next thing I noticed was my entire inventory was empty.
